<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Order Confirmation</title>
</head>

<body>
    <h1>Order Confirmation from Normandy Candles Studio</h1>

    <p>Dear {{customerName}},</p>

    <p>Thank you for placing an order with Normandy Candles Studio. We are pleased to confirm that your order has been received and is currently being processed. Below are the details of your order:</p>
    <h2>Order Details:</h2>
    <ul>
        <li><strong>Order Number:</strong> {{orderNumber}}</li>
        <li><strong>Order Date:</strong> {{orderDate}}</li>
        <li><strong>Total Order Value:</strong> {{totalOrderValue}}</li>
    </ul>
    <p><strong>Payment Method:</strong>Cash on delivery</p>
    <h2>Shipping Address:</h2>
    <p>
        <strong>Recipient Name:</strong> {{recipientName}}<br>
        <strong>Shipping Address:</strong> {{address}}<br>
        <strong>Contact Phone Number:</strong> {{contactPhoneNumber}}
    </p>
    <p>We appreciate your business and look forward to providing you with excellent service. Thank you for choosing Normandy Candles Studio.</p>
    <p>Warm regards,<br>
      Normandy Candles Studio<br>
</body>
       
</html>
